# Repo shape

- apps/
  - api/ (NestJS)
  - ui/ (Next.js)
  - workflows/ (Temporal)
- packages/ are reusable libraries. apps/* are deployables.

## Workspace conventions

- Prefer running scripts from repo root using pnpm filtering.

